descript.abstract: 5 meter contour lines out to 200 mile EEZ boundary. This file was interpolated from the 200m Teale bathymetric grid (bd200mv_2) with ESRI Spatial Analyst 8.1.
descript.purpose: Identification of depth variations through EEZ.
descript.supplinf:
Converted to California Teale Albers NAD 83 by the California Department of Fish and Game, Marine GIS
This file draws slowly because of the number of contour lines.
